    "Photon": "光子",
    ": A particle (quantum) of electromagnetic radiation; energy = h╬╜.": "：电磁辐射的粒子（量子）；能量 = hν。",
    "Quantum Mechanical Model": "量子力学模型",
    ": The modern model of the atom that treats electrons as waves and defines probability regions (orbitals).": "：将电子视为波并定义概率区域（轨道）的现代原子模型。",
    "Heisenberg Uncertainty Principle": "海森堡测不准原理",
