    ": Key Feature": "：关键特征",
    ": Half-life is constant ΓÇö it does not change regardless of the amount of sample.": "：半衰期是常数 —— 无论样本量多少，它都不会改变。",
    "Setting Up Conversions": "设置换算",
    "Multi-step Conversion": "多步换算",
    ": Some conversions require more than one conversion factor chained together.": "：某些换算需要将多个换算因子链接在一起。",
    "Unit Cancellation": "单位抵消",
    ": When a unit appears in both numerator and denominator, it cancels out.": "：当单位同时出现在分子和分母中时，它会被抵消。",
