    "Trailing Zeros": "尾随零",
    "Exact Numbers": "精确数字",
    ": Numbers obtained by counting or by definition have unlimited significant figures.": "：通过计数或定义获得的数字具有无限的有效数字。",
    ": The number 'a' in scientific notation; must be between 1 and 10.": "：科学计数法中的数字 'a'；必须在 1 和 10 之间。",
    "Exponent": "指数",
