    "1. Define the problem and what outcome you want to estimate.": "1. 定义问题和你想要估计的结果。",
    "180°: (x, y) → (−x, −y)": "180°：(x, y) → (−x, −y)",
    "2. Choose a model that has the same probabilities as the real situation.": "2. 选择一个与实际情况概率相同的模型。",
    "270° counterclockwise (or 90° clockwise): (x, y) → (y, −x)": "270°逆时针（或90°顺时针）：(x, y) → (y, −x)",
    "3. Run many trials of the simulation.": "3. 运行多次模拟试验。",
    "4. Collect and analyze the results.": "4. 收集并分析结果。",
    "5. Draw conclusions about the real situation.": "5. 对实际情况得出结论。",
