    "Work rate: combined rate = 1/t₁ + 1/t₂.": "工作速率：合速率= 1/t₁ + 1/t₂。",
    "Continuous at a: lim(x→a⁻) f(x) = lim(x→a⁺) f(x) = f(a).": "在a处连续：lim(x→a⁻) f(x) = lim(x→a⁺) f(x) = f(a)。",
    "Even function: f(-x) = f(x). Graph symmetric about y-axis.": "偶函数：f(-x) = f(x)。图像关于y轴对称。",
    "Infinite discontinuity: Vertical asymptote present.": "无穷间断：存在竖直渐近线。",
    "Jump discontinuity: Left and right limits exist but not equal.": "跳跃间断：左右极限存在但不相等。",
    "Odd function: f(-x) = -f(x). Graph symmetric about origin.": "奇函数：f(-x) = -f(x)。图像关于原点对称。",
    "One-to-one: Each y-value has exactly one x-value.": "一一对应：每个y值恰好对应一个x值。",
    "Onto: Every y-value in codomain has at least one x-value.": "映上：陪域中的每个y值至少有一个x值。",
    "Removable discontinuity: Hole at point, limit exists.": "可去间断：点处有洞，极限存在。",
    "Horizontal compression by factor b: f(x) → f(bx).": "水平压缩因子b：f(x) → f(bx)。",
    "Horizontal shift left by c: f(x) → f(x+c).": "向左水平移动c：f(x) → f(x+c)。",
    "Horizontal shift right by c: f(x) → f(x-c).": "向右水平移动c：f(x) → f(x-c)。",
    "Horizontal stretch by factor 1/b: f(x) → f(x/b).": "水平拉伸因子1/b：f(x) → f(x/b)。",
    "Reflect about x-axis: f(x) → -f(x).": "关于x轴反射：f(x) → -f(x)。",
    "Reflect about y-axis: f(x) → f(-x).": "关于y轴反射：f(x) → f(-x)。",
    "Vertical compression by factor 1/a: f(x) → f(x)/a.": "垂直压缩因子1/a：f(x) → f(x)/a。",
    "Vertical shift down by c: f(x) → f(x) - c.": "向下垂直移动c：f(x) → f(x) - c。",
    "Vertical shift up by c: f(x) → f(x) + c.": "向上垂直移动c：f(x) → f(x) + c。",
    "Vertical stretch by factor a: f(x) → a·f(x).": "垂直拉伸因子a：f(x) → a·f(x)。",
    "Degree of numerator < degree of denominator: y = 0 asymptote.": "分子次数<分母次数：y = 0渐近线。",
    "Degree of numerator = degree of denominator: y = leading coeff ratio.": "分子次数=分母次数：y =主导系数比。",
    "Degree of numerator > degree of denominator: No horizontal asymptote.": "分子次数>分母次数：没有水平渐近线。",
    "Hole (removable discontinuity): Factor and cancel.": "洞（可去间断）：因式分解并约去。",
    "Oblique asymptote: Numerator degree = denominator degree + 1.": "斜渐近线：分子次数=分母次数+ 1。",
    "Sign analysis: Test values in each interval.": "符号分析：在每个区间测试值。",
    "Simplify before analyzing, cancel common factors.": "在分析前简化，约去公因数。",
    "Vertical asymptote: Set denominator = 0, solve for x.": "竖直渐近线：令分母= 0，解出x。",
    "Annual percentage yield: APY = (1 + r/n)^n - 1.": "年百分比收益率：APY = (1 + r/n)^n - 1。",
    "Compound interest: A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt).": "复利：A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)。",
    "Continuous compound: A = Pe^(rt).": "连续复利：A = Pe^(rt)。",
    "Continuous growth: A(t) = A₀eᵏᵗ.": "连续增长：A(t) = A₀eᵏᵗ。",
    "Doubling time: A(t) = A₀ × 2^(t/doubling time).": "倍增时间：A(t) = A₀ × 2^(t/倍增时间)。",
    "Exponential decay model: A(t) = A₀(1 - r)ᵗ.": "指数衰减模型：A(t) = A₀(1 - r)ᵗ。",
    "Exponential growth model: A(t) = A₀(1 + r)ᵗ.": "指数增长模型：A(t) = A₀(1 + r)ᵗ。",
    "Half-life: Amount = Initial × (1/2)^(t/half-life).": "半衰期：数量=初始× (1/2)^(t/半衰期)。",
    "Change of base: logₐ(b) = log(b)/log(a).": "换底：logₐ(b) = log(b)/log(a)。",
    "Domain of log: Argument must be positive.": "对数的定义域：参数必须为正。",
    "Expand: log(2x³√y) = log(2) + 3log(x) + (1/2)log(y).": "展开：log(2x³√y) = log(2) + 3log(x) + (1/2)log(y)。",
    "Inverse of exponent: If bˣ = a, then x = logₐ(b).": "指数的反：如果bˣ = a，那么x = logₐ(b)。",
    "One-to-one property: logₐ(m) = logₐ(n) ⟹ m = n.": "一一对应性：logₐ(m) = logₐ(n) ⟹ m = n。",
    "Power rule: log(aᵇ) = b·log(a).": "幂法则：log(aᵇ) = b·log(a)。",
    "Product rule: log(ab) = log(a) + log(b).": "乘法法则：log(ab) = log(a) + log(b)。",
    "Quotient rule: log(a/b) = log(a) - log(b).": "商法则：log(a/b) = log(a) - log(b)。",
