    "Quotient: tan(θ) = sin(θ)/cos(θ).": "商：tan(θ) = sin(θ)/cos(θ)。",
    "Reciprocal: csc(θ) = 1/sin(θ), sec(θ) = 1/cos(θ).": "倒数：csc(θ) = 1/sin(θ)，sec(θ) = 1/cos(θ)。",
    "Sum identity: sin(α±β) = sin(α)cos(β) ± cos(α)sin(β).": "和恒等式：sin(α±β) = sin(α)cos(β) ± cos(α)sin(β)。",
