    "Reference angle: Acute angle to x-axis in standard position.": "参考角：标准位置到x轴的锐角。",
    "Unit circle: x² + y² = 1, (cos(θ), sin(θ)).": "单位圆：x² + y² = 1，(cos(θ)，sin(θ))。",
    "degrees = (radians × 180)/π.": "度数= (弧度× 180)/π。",
