    "Argument: θ = arctan(b/a), adjusted for quadrant.": "幅角：θ = arctan(b/a)，根据象限调整。",
    "Complex number: z = a + bi in rectangular, z = r(cos(θ) + i sin(θ)) in polar.": "复数：z = a + bi（直角），z = r(cos(θ) + i sin(θ))（极坐标）。",
    "Division in polar: (r₁∠θ₁)/(r₂∠θ₂) = (r₁/r₂)∠(θ₁-θ₂).": "极坐标相除：(r₁∠θ₁)/(r₂∠θ₂) = (r₁/r₂)∠(θ₁-θ₂)。",
    "Euler's formula: e^(iθ) = cos(θ) + i sin(θ).": "欧拉公式：e^(iθ) = cos(θ) + i sin(θ)。",
    "Modulus: |z| = √(a² + b²) = r.": "模：|z| = √(a² + b²) = r。",
