    "Angle between vectors: cos(θ) = (u·v)/(|u||v|).": "向量间夹角：cos(θ) = (u·v)/(|u||v|)。",
    "Component of v in direction of u: (v·u)/|u|.": "v在u方向的分量：(v·u)/|u|。",
    "Dot product: u·v = u₁v₁ + u₂v₂ = |u||v|cos(θ).": "点积：u·v = u₁v₁ + u₂v₂ = |u||v|cos(θ)。",
    "Linear combination: c₁u + c₂v (adding vectors).": "线性组合：c₁u + c₂v（向量相加）。",
    "Orthogonal vectors: u·v = 0.": "正交向量：u·v = 0。",
    "Unit vector: û = u/|u|.": "单位向量：û = u/|u|。",
    "Vector magnitude: |⟨a,b⟩| = √(a² + b²).": "向量大小：|⟨a,b⟩| = √(a² + b²)。",
