    "Arc length: L = ∫√((dx/dt)² + (dy/dt)²) dt.": "弧长：L = ∫√((dx/dt)² + (dy/dt)²) dt。",
    "Cycloid: x = r(t - sin(t)), y = r(1 - cos(t)).": "摆线：x = r(t - sin(t))，y = r(1 - cos(t))。",
    "Derivative: dy/dx = (dy/dt)/(dx/dt).": "导数：dy/dx = (dy/dt)/(dx/dt)。",
    "Eliminate parameter: Solve one equation for t, substitute in other.": "消去参数：从一个方程解出t，代入另一个。",
