    "AC method: Find factors of AC that add to B.": "AC法：找AC的因数，相加等于B。",
    "Difference of cubes: a³ - b³ = (a-b)(a² + ab + b²).": "立方差：a³ - b³ = (a-b)(a² + ab + b²)。",
