    "Equations with rational expressions. Find the LCD of all denominators. Multiply every term by the LCD to clear denominators. Solve the resulting polynomial equation. Always check solutions in the original equation.": "Equations with 有理 expressions. Find the LCD of all denominators. 乘 every term by the LCD to clear denominators. 解 the resulting 多项式 equation. Always check 解 in the original equation.",
