    "Find vertical asymptotes and holes. Find horizontal asymptotes. Find x-intercepts and y-intercept. Plot several test points. Sketch smoothly, respecting asymptotes and approaching them asymptotically.": "Find vertical asymptotes and holes. Find horizontal asymptotes. Find x-intercepts and y-intercept. Plot several test points. Sketch smoothly, respecting asymptotes and approaching them asymptotically.",
    "Find where revenue equals cost. Set profit function equal to zero or set revenue equal to expense. The intersection point is the break-even point.": "Find 其中 revenue 等于 cost. Set profit 函数 equal to 零 or set revenue equal to expense. The 交点 point is the break-even point.",
