    "Functions": "Functions",
    "Functions can be combined through addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. Composition of functions (f ∘ g)(x) = f(g(x)) means apply g first, then apply f to the result.": "Functions can be combined through addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. 复合 of functions (f ∘ g)(x) = f(g(x)) means apply g first, 那么 apply f to the result.",
    "Functions of the form f(x) = ax² + bx + c where a ≠ 0. The graph is a parabola (U-shaped curve). The coefficient a determines the direction: a > 0 opens upward, a": "Functions of the form f(x) = ax² + bx + c 其中 a ≠ 0. The 绘制图像 is a 抛物线 (U-shaped curve). The coefficient a determines the direction: a > 0 向上开口, a",
