    "Given a_1 and r, find any term using a_n = a_1 · r^{n-1}. Common ratio: r = a_{n+1}/a_n. Handle negative ratios (alternating sign sequences). To insert geometric means between two terms, compute appropriate r and generate intermediates.": "Given a_1 and r, find any term using a_n = a_1 · r^{n-1}. Common ratio: r = a_{n+1}/a_n. Handle 负数 ratios (alternating sign sequences). To insert 几何 means between two terms, compute appropriate r and generate intermediates.",
    "Given probability, find the value. Example: Find c such that P(X": "Given probability, find the value. 例子: Find c 使得 P(X",
