    "Higher-degree polynomials appear in optimization in calculus. Taylor series approximate functions using polynomials. Interpolation fits n points with degree n-1 polynomial.": "Higher-度 polynomials appear in optimization in calculus. Taylor 级数 approximate functions using polynomials. Interpolation fits n points with 度 n-1 多项式.",
