    "Multiply by the reciprocal: (P/Q) ÷ (R/S) = (P/Q) × (S/R). Simplify as with multiplication. Important: the reciprocal's denominator is S, which must be non-zero.": "乘 by the reciprocal: (P/Q) ÷ (R/S) = (P/Q) × (S/R). 简化 as with multiplication. Important: the reciprocal's 分母 is S, which must be non-零.",
    "Multiply one or both equations by constants so that one variable has opposite coefficients. Add the equations to eliminate that variable, leaving one equation with one unknown.": "乘 one or both equations by constants so that one variable has opposite coefficients. 加 the equations to eliminate that variable, leaving one equation with one unknown.",
