    "Solve one equation for a variable, then substitute that expression into the other equation. This reduces the system to one equation with one variable.": "解 one equation 对于 a variable, 那么 substitute that expression into the other equation. This reduces the system to one equation with one variable.",
    "Solve one equation for t, substitute into other. Example: x = 2t + 1, y = t² → t = (x-1)/2 → y = ((x-1)/2)². Check for domain/range restrictions preserved in conversion.": "解 one equation 对于 t, substitute into other. 例子: x = 2t + 1, y = t² → t = (x-1)/2 → y = ((x-1)/2)². Check 对于 定义域/值域 restrictions preserved in conversion.",
