    "Specify interval like [0, 2π] to list finite. For x ∈ [0, 2π], sin x = 1/2 has solutions x = π/6, 5π/6. Check domain restrictions (tan x undefined at π/2, etc.).": "Specify interval like [0, 2π] to list finite. 对于 x ∈ [0, 2π], sin x = 1/2 has 解 x = π/6, 5π/6. Check 定义域 restrictions (tan x undefined at π/2, etc.).",
