    "Standard and Vertex Forms:": "Standard and 顶点 Forms:",
    "Standard form: f(x) = ax² + bx + c. Vertex form: f(x) = a(x-h)² + k, where (h,k) is the vertex. Vertex form makes the parabola's features immediately visible.": "Standard form: f(x) = ax² + bx + c. 顶点 form: f(x) = a(x-h)² + k, 其中 (h,k) is the 顶点. 顶点 form makes the 抛物线's features immediately visible.",
    "Step-by-Step Process:": "步骤-by-步骤 Process:",
    "Substitute a, b, c correctly (watch signs!). Simplify the discriminant first. The ± symbol means we find two values. Always check if the radicand is negative.": "Substitute a, b, c correctly (watch signs!). 简化 the discriminant first. The ± symbol means we find two values. Always check 如果 the radicand is 负数.",
    "Substitute the x and y values into both original equations. The solution is correct if both equations are satisfied.": "Substitute the x and y values into both original equations. The 解 is correct 如果 both equations are satisfied.",
