    "Sum of terms in a sequence. Arithmetic series: a_1 + a_2 + ... + a_n. Geometric series: a_1 + a_1r + a_1r^2 + ... + a_1r^{n-1}. Infinite series: sum of infinitely many terms (may or may not converge).": "和 of terms in a 数列. 算术 级数: a_1 + a_2 + ... + a_n. 几何 级数: a_1 + a_1r + a_1r^2 + ... + a_1r^{n-1}. Infinite 级数: 和 of infinitely many terms (may or may not converge).",
