    "Test H₀ (null hypothesis) vs Hₐ (alternative). Type I error: reject H₀ when true (α significance level). Type II error: fail to reject H₀ when false (β). p-value: probability of observing data as extreme given H₀ is true.": "Test H₀ (null hypothesis) vs Hₐ (alternative). Type I error: reject H₀ 当 true (α significance level). Type II error: fail to reject H₀ 当 false (β). p-value: probability of observing data as extreme given H₀ is true.",
