    "Unit Circle:": "Unit 圆:",
    "Use FOIL for binomials or the distributive property for general cases. FOIL: First, Outer, Inner, Last. For longer polynomials, multiply each term in the first by every term in the second.": "Use FOIL 对于 binomials or the distributive property 对于 general cases. FOIL: First, Outer, Inner, Last. 对于 longer polynomials, 乘 each term in the first by every term in the second.",
    "Use exponential (inverse) form: if log_b(x) = k, then x = b^k. Properties of logarithms can condense or expand terms before converting to exponential form.": "Use exponential (反函数) form: 如果 log_b(x) = k, 那么 x = b^k. Properties of logarithms can condense or 展开 terms before converting to exponential form.",
    "Use inequality notation for intervals. Solution might be x": "Use inequality notation 对于 intervals. 解 might be x",
    "Use x = -b/(2a) to find the x-coordinate of the vertex. Substitute into f(x) to find the y-coordinate. Vertex (h,k) is the extreme point of the parabola.": "Use x = -b/(2a) to find the x-coordinate of the 顶点. Substitute into f(x) to find the y-coordinate. 顶点 (h,k) is the extreme point of the 抛物线.",
    "Use z-test when σ known and n large. Use t-test when σ unknown (more common). t-distribution has fatter tails than normal, especially for small n.": "Use z-test 当 σ known and n large. Use t-test 当 σ unknown (more common). t-distribution has fatter tails than normal, especially 对于 small n.",
