    "Vector has magnitude and direction: v = ⟨a, b⟩ = ai + bj. Magnitude |v| = √(a² + b²). Unit vector: u = v/|v|. Zero vector 0 = ⟨0, 0⟩. Position vector from origin to point (a, b).": "Vector has magnitude and direction: v = ⟨a, b⟩ = ai + bj. Magnitude |v| = √(a² + b²). Unit vector: u = v/|v|. 零 vector 0 = ⟨0, 0⟩. Position vector from origin to point (a, b).",
